  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK887">
<l>ceppiṉ puṇarccipōṟ kūṭiṉuṅ kūṭātē </l>
<l>yuṭpakai yuṟṟa kuṭi</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Never indeed will a family subject to internal hatred unite (really) though it may present an apparent union like that of a casket and its lid.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
